Class Candle

java.lang.Object
  gft.api.Candle
All Implemented Interfaces:
common.util.storable.Storable
public class Candle
extends java.lang.Object
implements common.util.storable.Storable

Represents Candle: an aggregated information about prices within the given period of time.

A candle is characterized with:

  • type (see getType())
  • instrument (see getInstrumentId())
  • start timestamp (see getStartTimestamp())
  • open (see getOpen())
  • close (see getClose())
  • high (see getHigh())
  • low (see getLow())

Author:
Boris Malkin
